01:51.520 --> 01:52.976
- Trust me, trust me.

01:53.030 --> 01:55.066
This is one of my best ideas.

01:55.110 --> 01:57.101
Oh, here here here.
This is the place.

01:57.150 --> 01:58.731
- [Wendell] May I remind
you that all your ideas

01:58.780 --> 02:01.112
haye so far resulted
In total failure?

